div.p: Mechanism: Non-blocking status collection of orphaned children. sizeof=Task Table Row (~1.2KB)

ul.li: WNOHANG (0x01): Ensures PID 1 does not block if no children are dead.
-1 Target: Reaps any child that has changed state (orphans adopted by Init).
Memory Cleanup: Kernel removes task_struct and stack only after this call.
